item.title: CVE-2023-39440|2024-10-08T16:25:51.455Z -- sap_se -- sap%20businessobjects%20business%20intelligence
item.description: In SAP BusinessObjects Business Intelligence - version 420, If a user logs in to a particular program, under certain specific conditions memory might not be cleared up properly, due to which attacker might be able to get access to user credentials. For a successful attack, the attacker needs to have local access to the system. There is no impact on availability and integrity.
